# API Testing Portfolio - Authentication (Reqres)

This project demonstrates API testing for authentication using Reqres.

## Scope
- Login functionality testing
- Positive and negative scenarios
- Input validation
- Error handling
- Basic security testing

## Tools Used
- Postman
- GitHub

## Test Coverage
- Valid login
- Missing fields
- Invalid credentials
- Edge cases
- Injection attempt

This project complements UI test cases by validating backend behavior.
